Revision history for Perl extension Map::Tube::Paris

0.2.2 2026-06-26
  - Fixed Makefile.PL issue preventing data file from being installed.
  - Improvements to Makefile.PL
  - Switched to Github as code repository and issue handler.

0.2.1 2026-06-11
  - Removed code signatures (cpansign is deprecated), replaced with Sigstore/cosign.
  - Prepared for use with Map::Tube v5.0.1.

0.2.0 2025-12-15
  - Added newly opened funicular C1.

0.1.1 2025-04-30
  - Require Map::Tube 4.09.
  - Remove -T from shebangs in tests (in accordance with Map::Tube 4.09).

0.1.0 2025-04-29
  - Initial release
